{"tid":320426,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"范冰冰美國告郭文貴","createTime":"2017-07-13T13:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T14:38:41.000Z","uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a6e1b50bcfd074a88b72699eadabf52350be65e","tid":320426,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:48:18.000Z","msg":"逃亡海外富商郭文貴早前爆料稱，多名內地女星涉及桃色醜聞。其中一名被點名的女星范冰冰在微博宣布，已委託律師在美國起訴郭文貴，並要求他與相關平台立即停止散布不實信息。<br />\n<br />\n范冰冰在微博貼出其工作室的聲明，澄清郭文貴發表與她相關的言論「屬憑空捏造，係對范冰冰女士的惡意誹謗」。工作室指，范已委託美國律師，在美國起訴郭文貴，要求他和相關平台立即停止發布不實信息，停止惡意轉載、擴散傳播，並向范承擔一切法律責任。<br />\n<br />\n范冰冰日前已在微博回應郭文貴的指控，指「我就站在陽光下等着你，等你從黑暗裏走出來與我對峙！我從不缺少面對黑暗的勇氣！從前是，現在是！將來亦然！」而另一個被郭文貴點名指涉桃色醜聞的女星許晴，上周五（7日）亦已發表聲明要求他公開道歉，並稱已委託律師，向郭文貴追究法律責任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170713/s00004/1499932311047\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170713%2Fs00004%2F1499932311047&d=IKE5B3xalFjF69%2F32X2WuZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=02d89fab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170713%2Fs00004%2F1499932311047&h=f30b022a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170713/s00004/1499932311047</a><br />\n<br />\n幾時有片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ac8989a867746028d33d8fb84da0d44c21757a1","tid":320426,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:49:33.000Z","msg":"連范冰冰都逼佢po片，我們有福了"},{"pid":"0fceb65542204dd8e12ae0b581c53a0a54e9fa62","tid":320426,"uid":16034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:53:18.000Z","msg":"想當年.. 「移花接木」..."},{"pid":"20c976644884a8d0ef54e3e7c0cdc0aec1d607dd","tid":